OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FHeavy rain will move south
OL,6,Ftoday, followed by blustery wintry
OL,7,Fshowers across the north. Dry at first
OL,8,Fin the south, but turning increasingly
OL,9,Fcloud with rain arriving later.
OL,10,FFeeling chilly in the strengthening
OL,11,Fwinds, with gales around some northern
OL,12,Fcoasts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain clears south this
OL,15,Fevening, followed by drier weather in
OL,16,Fthe south with clear spells. Blustery
OL,17,Fshowers continue in the north with
OL,18,Fsnow over hills. Chilly with a patchy
OL,19,Ffrost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
