OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FSunny spells and showers in
OL,6,Fthe north, but these easing in the
OL,7,Fafternoon with hazy sunshine. Drier in
OL,8,Fthe south with just the odd shower and
OL,9,Fhazy sunshine. Windy.
